            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "深水埗獨行賊扮客搶走值15萬勞力士 跳乘小巴逃去",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"探員到場調查。林思明攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/e8fc90c7d4e0a54c5753462f54c86efe/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250409/_2025040916514913256.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">探員到場調查。林思明攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>深水埗長沙灣道169號一間售賣金飾二手錶店舖，今(9日)下午2時52分，女職員報案指，一名年約50多歲男子走入店內選購手錶，期間着店東拿出一隻約值15萬元的勞力士116520型號手錶，他趁店東未有為意，突然搶走手錶走出門外，跳上一部往旺角的小巴逃去，職員追出無果，報警求助。探員到場調查，翻看閉路電視追緝賊人。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185692/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"探員向負責人及女職員問話。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/131e0704e01adefee49ae678c4d56509/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250409_162957890.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        探員向負責人及女職員問話。林思明攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185693/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"探員到場調查。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8f3694f2ce109756e29737c59e04600a/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250409_163128107.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div c